### Submit text job
POST {{API_URL}}/api/jobs/text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Summarise today's top AI news.",
  "params": { "temperature": 0.7 },
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "projectId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
}

### Get job status
GET {{API_URL}}/api/jobs/{{jobId}}

### Retry job
POST {{API_URL}}/api/jobs/{{jobId}}/retry

### Admin usage
GET {{API_URL}}/api/admin/usage
x-admin-token: {{JWT_SIGNING_KEY}}
